  <h1>Contact</h1>

  <div class="bio">
    <p>I read everything that comes in. I reply selectively — usually within a week, sometimes never. Not personal; it's the only way I keep the signal up.</p>

    <p>Good reasons to email: a project you want to build together, a piece of writing here you have a sharp opinion about, a job or collaboration where the work is <em>specific</em>, a recommendation for something I should read or look at, or — best of all — telling me I'm wrong about something.</p>

    <p>Less good: cold pitches that could've gone to anyone with a contact form.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="links">
    {% for link in site.links %}
    <a href="{{ link.url }}"{% if "http" in link.url %} rel="me noopener" target="_blank"{% endif %}>{{ link.label }}</a>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</section>
